moveList.moveDescription: The target is physically pounded with a long tail or a foreleg, etc.
A chopping attack with a high critical-hit ratio.
Although each slap is weak, this attack hits the target two to five times in succession.
The target is hit with a flurry of punches that strike two to five times in a row.
A Normal-type attack move. It is highly accurate and relatively powerful.
A move that also nets money at the end of battle. How much depends on the attack frequency and level.
A fiery punch. May cause a burn.
An icy punch. May cause freezing.
An electric punch. It may paralyze.
Scratches with sharp claws.
Grips with powerful pincers.
A powerful pincer attack that may cause fainting.
Blades of wind hit the foe on the 2nd turn. It has a high critical-hit ratio.
A frenetic dance to uplift the fighting spirit. This raises the user’s offensive stats.
The target is cut with a scythe or claw.
A gust of wind is whipped up by wings and launched at the target to inflict damage.
The user sticks its head out and rams straight forward. It may make the foe flinch.
A full-body charge attack.
A reckless, full-body charge attack for slamming into the target. This also damages the user a little.
A reckless, life-risking tackle in which the user rushes the target. This also damages the user.
The user bites the target with viciously sharp fangs to inflict damage.
The user growls in a cute way, making the foe lower its Attack. stat.
The user curls up to conceal weak spots and raise its Defense stat.
The user temporarily empties its mind to forget its concerns. This sharply raises the user's Sp. Def stat.
The user chomps hard on the target with its sharp front fangs. This cuts the target's HP in half.
Raises Attack and Defense at the expense of Speed. It works differently for the Ghost type.
The user continually rolls into the target over five turns. It becomes more powerful each time it hits.
The user crunches up the target with sharp fangs. This may also lower the target's Defense stat.
The target is taunted into a rage that allows it to use only attack moves for three turns.
The user attacks the target with great power. However, this also lowers the user's Attack and Defense stats.
The user lets loose a huge yawn that lulls the target into falling asleep on the next turn.
